            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/6YPNLBGUhdCT4LxEJMqIgw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEC5E1KQ_M.jpg\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Investing.com -</strong>周五，3月6日，港股三大指數集體走高，恒生科技指數大升3%，科網股領升。京東 (HK:9618)、攜程集團 (HK:9961)雙雙升超7%，美圖公司 (HK:1357)升超6%，網易-S (HK:9999)升超5%，小米集團－Ｗ (HK:1810)、阿里巴巴-SW (HK:9988)升超3%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">國金證券表示，美元流動性收緊，疊加春節前後，外賣、紅包補貼進一步加劇對互聯網巨頭企業盈利性的擔憂，導致恒生科技近期持續回檔。但我們依舊看好AI產業趨勢&amp;提效邏輯，而互聯網巨頭是真正有資源、數據、場景及現金流去落地主要公司，積極關注互聯網巨頭公司業績表現及AI相關業務落地進展。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:undefined;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.investing.com/pro/pricing?utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_source=yahoo&amp;utm_campaign=yahoo-hk\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">undefined</a></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%81%92%E7%A7%91%E6%8C%87%E5%A4%A7%E5%8D%873-%E7%A7%91%E7%B6%B2%E8%82%A1%E9%A0%98%E5%8D%87-%E4%BA%AC%E6%9D%B1-%E6%94%9C%E7%A8%8B%E5%8D%87%E8%B6%857-%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%B3-042206577.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-06 13:21:30",
